'''Telmo Emanuel Gomes Arcanjo''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈtɛl.mu e.mɐ.nu.ˈɛl ˈɡo.mɨz ɐɾ.ˈkɐ̃.ʒu|lang}}; born 21 June 2001) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] or [[winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Vitória S.C.]] Born in Portugal, he plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
Arcanjo made his professional debut with [[C.D. Tondela|Tondela]] in a 3–2 [[Primeira Liga]] loss to [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] on 14 July 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/07/14/portugal/portuguese-liga-/gil-vicente-fc/cd-tondela/3064928/|title=Gil Vicente vs. Tondela - 14 July 2020|website=Soccerway}}</ref>

On 16 June 2023, Vitória SC announced the free signing of Arcanjo on a four-year deal.<ref>{{Cite web |date=16 June 2023 |title=Telmo Arcanjo é do Vitória até 2027 - Vitória Sport Clube |trans-title=Telmo Arcanjo to Vitória until 2027 - Vitória Sport Clube |url=https://vitoriasc.pt/2023/06/16/telmo-arcanjo-e-do-vitoria-ate-2027/ |access-date=11 July 2023 |publisher=Vitória SC |language=pt-PT}}</ref> On 10 January 2026, Arcanjo played in the Portuguese [[Taça da Liga]] final against [[S.C. Braga|Braga]] in which [[Vitória S.C.|Vitória Guimarães]] won 2-1.

==International career==
Born in Portugal, Arcanjo is of Cape Verdean descent. He represented the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde U19]]s in a friendly 2–0 loss to the [[Portugal national under-19 football team|Portugal U19]]s on 30 January 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fpf.pt/selecoes/futebol-masculino/selecao-sub-19/jogos/ficha-de-jogo/match/1359450|title=Seleção Sub-19 - Ficha de Jogo, resultados e equipas &#124; FPF|website=www.fpf.pt}}</ref> He was called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] for a pair of friendlies in June 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://inforpress.cv/football-newcomers-sixten-mohlin-joao-correia-rely-cabral-and-alexis-goncalves-are-new-in-bubistas-call-up/|title=Football: Newcomers Sixten Mohlin, João Correia, Rely Cabral and Alexis Gonçalves are new in Bubista's call-up &#124; INFORPRESS|date=27 May 2021|access-date=9 June 2021|archive-date=30 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130204751/https://inforpress.cv/football-newcomers-sixten-mohlin-joao-correia-rely-cabral-and-alexis-goncalves-are-new-in-bubistas-call-up/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He debuted with the Cape Verde national team in a friendly 2–0 loss to [[Senegal national football team|Senegal]] on 8 June 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://globalsportsarchive.com/match/soccer/2021-06-08/senegal-vs-cape-verde-islands/2376236/|title=Match Report of Senegal vs Cape Verde Islands - 2021-06-08 - FIFA Friendlies - Global Sports Archive|website=globalsportsarchive.com}}</ref>

