==Personal life==
Arcanjo is the brother of the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde]] international footballer [[Fábio Arcanjo]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://criolosports.com/index.php/criolos-no-estrangeiro/5789-criolos-no-estrangeiro-futebol-portugal-telmo-arcanjo-reforca-juniores-do-tondela|title=Criolos no Estrangeiro: Futebol Portugal – Telmo Arcanjo reforça juniores do Tondela|website=criolosports.com|access-date=21 July 2020|archive-date=21 July 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721165349/https://criolosports.com/index.php/criolos-no-estrangeiro/5789-criolos-no-estrangeiro-futebol-portugal-telmo-arcanjo-reforca-juniores-do-tondela|url-status=dead}}</ref>

